Now how do you put it together. What you do is

00:01:42.380 --> 00:01:47.280
you thread the microphone capsule in
through the little clasp

00:01:47.280 --> 00:01:50.890
making sure that you fit it into the

00:01:50.890 --> 00:01:57.110
manufactured grooves. Once you've got that in place it's quite firm.

00:01:57.110 --> 00:02:00.460
Then you can

00:02:00.460 --> 00:02:05.060
fit the little microphone windscreen
and it has a little manufactured groove

00:02:05.060 --> 00:02:05.950
to settle in

00:02:05.950 --> 00:02:09.950
once you've done that

00:02:09.950 --> 00:02:14.629
you can set up the cable restraint.
Open up the clip

00:02:14.629 --> 00:02:17.870
and thread in the cable making sure
that it goes

00:02:17.870 --> 00:02:22.620
inside the clip and then very carefully

00:02:22.620 --> 00:02:25.690
role the cable are over so it goes

00:02:25.690 --> 00:02:29.989
